ActIndian Act
SubjectSaik’uz First Nation ** absolute surrender **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to accept the absolute surrender with conditions made to Her Majesty in right of Canada by SAIK’UZ FIRST NATION of a portion of Stony Creek Indian Reserve No. 1, Laketown Indian Reserve No. 3 and Old Country Meadow Indian Reserve No. 4, located approximately 200 kilometers west of Prince George, British Columbia.
